kdna-react provides React components and hooks for building
KDNA-integrated web applications. Components handle file selection,
load-plan state, password entry, license activation, asset inspection,
and server-mediated asset loading.

This package reuses @aikdna/kdna-web-client for browser networking, bounded
public projections, safe errors, LoadPlan management, and Runtime Capsule
validation. Decryption and authoritative license verification are delegated to
a compatible server such as @aikdna/kdna-web-server.

